  "id": "RAW_b3de6e0d",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-10）：微软开源 UserLM，专攻对话中用户角色模拟，推动真实交互技术落地",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247499700&idx=1&sn=1c4da48dc190682c72d338b15c3d10bd",
  "date": "2025-10-10 10:16:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：UserLM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" data-height=\"658\" data-imgfileid=\"100016040\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9a96891b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyhlf39gyrG58gYy4Yu2MhICFcFSTgtvy7WfPuoq8wk0HXYzhVsiaDkXYMQYLsj2IdZKUjice9vf7Jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">★</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">UserLM-8b 是一个由微软开发的语言模型，旨在模拟对话中的“用户”角色。与典型的助手型大模型不同，UserLM-8b 通过预测用户在对话中的发言来实现更真实的对话模拟。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">这对于开发更强大的对话助手非常有用。模型可以根据任务意图生成用户的初始发言、后续发言，并在对话结束时生成结束标记。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/userlm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/userlm</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Lumina-DiMOO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" data-height=\"644\" data-imgfileid=\"100016037\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3f1b693&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyhlf39gyrG58gYy4Yu2MhIoNJicGOsdOLLDSbIBjpibQcAWSDTOVuBOacV4Ke5yRmw3Y4hkibeZFuCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">★</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Lumina-DiMOO 是一个全方位的基础模型，专注于无缝的多模态生成和理解。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">完全离散的扩散建模</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够处理各种模态的输入和输出。Lumina-DiMOO 支持广泛的多模态任务，包括文本到图像生成、图像到图像生成（如图像编辑、主题驱动生成和图像修复等）以及高级图像理解。与之前的自回归或混合自回归-扩散范式相比，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Lumina-DiMOO 展示了显著的采样效率</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，并通过设计定制的缓存方法将采样速度提高了两倍。该模型在多个基准测试中实现了最先进的性能，超越了现有的开源统一多模态模型，树立了该领域的新标准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lumina-dimoo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lumina-dimoo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：CoDA-v0-Instruct</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43148148148148147\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"500\" data-imgfileid=\"100016036\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5fd4280e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyhlf39gyrG58gYy4Yu2MhIgA7gHF6icACDHl3AczpbJNlibfu2NRE2z200Ab8Xb3vfvfJQ2TTM5e8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">★</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">CoDA是由Salesforce AI Research开发的基于扩散的语言模型，专为强大的代码生成和双向上下文理解而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">CoDA利用离散扩散过程来理解过去和未来的标记，使其特别适合于代码补全和生成任务。该模型以轻量级但功能强大的形式发布，具有1.7B参数，优化用于代码生成任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/coda-v0-instruct\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/coda-v0-instruct</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：Jamba-Reasoning</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.575925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"668\" data-imgfileid=\"100016038\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89450836&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyhlf39gyrG58gYy4Yu2MhIRMtlPgbJ6eUA83lO5iaC2N2nUJt6Q511ecNV5KLwqwIo1Ug5eictmjKQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">★</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">AI21-Jamba-Reasoning-3B 是一款高性能的推理模型，专注于在智能基准测试中取得领先成绩，并在紧凑的3B架构中实现高效处理。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型结合了Transformer注意力机制和Mamba状态空间模型，优化了序列处理效率，能够在笔记本电脑、GPU甚至移动设备上流畅运行。它支持极长的上下文处理，适合边缘部署和数据中心工作负载。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ai21-jamba-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ai21-jamba-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Model Explorer ONNX</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.31574074074074077\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"366\" data-imgfileid=\"100016035\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1a3c3c9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyhlf39gyrG58gYy4Yu2MhIibOyTztibDvF6oy82qAuWy9wfvIDMuOuh6icapgZHDLfF9XictkibOZ5SgQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">★</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Model Explorer ONNX 是一个用于可视化 ONNX 模型的工具，其通过图形化的方式展示模型的输入、输出和节点，帮助用户更好地理解和分析模型结构。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该工具支持在 Windows 上通过 WSL 运行，并提供了多种颜色主题以增强可视化效果。此外，它还支持与 PyTorch 的 ONNX 导出器集成，允许用户验证和比较中间结果的准确性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/model-explorer-onnx\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/model-explorer-onnx</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Code2Video</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3731481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"432\" data-imgfileid=\"100016039\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11dc090a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyhlf39gyrG58gYy4Yu2MhIP5oEPxu6zRC3ZsZztY2uAiayqcuicicWpJU3T6DYialeVSDhd5MicMxJbOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">★</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Code2Video是一个以代码为中心的框架，用于从知识点生成高质量的教育视频，与基于像素的文本到视频模型不同，该方法利用可执行的Manim代码来确保视频的清晰性、一致性和可重现性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">其模块化设计包括计划者、编码者和评论者三个代理，协同工作以实现结构化生成。项目还推出了首个代码驱动的视频生成基准MMMC，涵盖117个精选学习主题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/code2video\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/code2video</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总了微软 UserLM、Lumina-DiMOO 等多项最新开源 AI 模型和工具，涵盖对话模拟、多模态生成、代码生成、推理优化及模型可视化等前沿领域。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总了微软 UserLM、Lumina-DiMOO 等多项最新开源 AI 模型和工具，涵盖对话模拟、多模态生成、代码生成、推理优化及模型可视化等前沿领域。",
  "summary": "文章精选并介绍了近期多项重要的开源 AI 项目，涵盖基座模型、框架平台和 Agent 开发等多个方面。其中包括微软开发的 UserLM，一个专为模拟对话中用户角色设计的语言模型，旨在提升对话助手的真实交互能力。Lumina-DiMOO 作为一个全方位的基础模型，展示了在无缝多模态生成与理解方面的卓越性能，通过离散扩散建模提升了采样效率。Salesforce AI Research 的 CoDA-v0-Instruct 则专注于高效的代码生成和双向上下文理解。此外，AI21 的 Jamba-Reasoning-3B 是一款结合 Transformer 和 Mamba 的高性能推理模型，支持超长上下文处理。文章还介绍了用于可视化 ONNX 模型的 Model Explorer ONNX 工具，以及 Code2Video 这一代码驱动的教育视频生成框架。这些项目共同展现了当前 AI 领域在模型、工具和应用层面的最新进展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "UserLM 开创对话 AI 用户角色模拟新范式",
      "explanation": "微软 UserLM 通过预测用户发言，提升对话系统模拟真实用户交互的能力，对开发更强大的对话助手具有重要意义。"
    },
